&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why this role is unique&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the &lt;strong&gt;General Ledger&lt;/strong&gt; for multiple German legal entities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure accurate financial reporting in line with &lt;strong&gt;IFRS&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;HGB&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to finance transformation and continuous process improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
