&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain the &lt;strong&gt;General Ledger&lt;/strong&gt; for German legal entities, ensuring transactions are recorded accurately and in line with Group accounting policies, IFRS, HGB and local statutory requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the preparation of statutory financial statements, annual audits and other local reporting requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare balance sheet reconciliations and ensure reconciling items are investigated and resolved.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with monthly &lt;strong&gt;VAT&lt;/strong&gt; returns and related tax compliance activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the global intercompany reconciliation process and collaborate with finance teams across the Group.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to system improvements and finance projects that enhance efficiency and strengthen internal controls.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
