&lt;li&gt;Solid knowledge of &lt;strong&gt;IFRS&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;HGB&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in &lt;strong&gt;General Ledger Accounting&lt;/strong&gt; or Legal Entity Accounting within a medium to large international organisation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with ERP systems; Workday Financials is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent German and English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
