&lt;p data-start=&quot;46&quot; data-end=&quot;493&quot;&gt;A career driven by you. Join&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;AutoScout24 Group&lt;/strong&gt; and experience life in the fast lane. We’re not just leading the market; we’re creating it. We’re constantly innovating, evolving and transforming things for our customers. We’re driven, ambitious and determined to do our best work, together. For a career that doesn’t stand still, where you can put your ideas in the driving seat and change the way the world moves, join our international community.&lt;/p&gt;
